App design sections: 
____________________________
  1. THE BACKEND
  * Fetch Categories
  * Fetch Brands
  * Fetch Products ( Create stream to reduce the reads and writes of firestore)
  * Add, remove wishlist items of each user
  * Add, update or remove user addresses
  * Add to cart ( from product care, single and variation product from product details )
  * Checkout and create orders. 

 2. THE CORE CONCEPTS
 *  Reusable light and dark theme
 *  Firebase Authentication, firestore and Storage
 * Shared Preferences - for local storage
 * GetX / Bloc State Management 